organic.title: Home, Public Defender Agency, State of Alaska
organic.snippet: Our mission is to provide constitutionally mandated legal representation to indigent clients appointed by the court. Logo link to home · Home ...

organic.title: Public Defender Agency - Alaska Department of Administration
organic.snippet: The Alaska Public Defender Agency provides legal representation to indigent clients. Terrence Haas is the Public Defender. Deputy Public Defenders are in Criminal, Civil, and Appellate divisions.

organic.title: Office of the Public Defender - District of Alaska | Federal Public ...
organic.snippet: The Office of the Public Defender for Alaska provides legal help for federal crimes statewide. They serve trial, appellate, and habeas cases. Jamie McGrady is the Federal Defender.

organic.title: Alaska Public Defender Agency
organic.snippet: The Alaska Public Defender Agency provides legal representation for felony, misdemeanor, child in need of aid, and juvenile delinquency cases. Call (907) 334-4400 or (800) 478-4404.

organic.title: State of Alaska – Alaska Public Defender Agency | SREC
organic.snippet: The Alaska Public Defender Agency offers legal help for defendants. Offices are in Juneau (907-465-4911), Ketchikan (907-228-8950), and Sitka (907-747-6808). Income requirements may apply.
